{"tid":94153,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"傳陳永棋明言不撐林鄭等於反中央","createTime":"2017-01-25T04:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T07:38:54.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"732f70caffc6461f3b18fc29351abdd2815c9412","tid":94153,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"傳陳永棋明言不撐林鄭等於反中央 中聯辦出面邀選委去造勢大會<br />\n<br />\n多名特首參選人正積極備戰，近日分別約見不同界別選委爭取提名，《明報》政情專欄「李先知」指，部分選委或建制派因收到中聯辦等機構或官員「溫馨提示」而支持林鄭，更引述有政治耳語謂，部分選委收到的林鄭2月3日造勢大會邀請，但並非由林鄭或其辦公室發出，而是由中聯辦副主任級官員出面，希望他們當日能出席。<br />\n<br />\n專欄又指，部分建制派重量級人士，亦在建制圈子發放林鄭已是中央選定的特首人選、支持其他人等於與中央對着幹等信息，更指全國政協常委的工業界（第二）選委陳永棋昨日分別與曾俊華及林鄭會面，上午與曾俊華會面時，稱與對方相識多時，過往有很多合作接觸等；到下午與林鄭的會面中，已表明自己「一定會提名」林鄭，更當面明言誰人不支持林鄭，是等於反對中央。<br />\n<br />\n專欄指中聯辦不時向選委表示中央屬意林鄭等信息，有選委一度於一日內收到中聯辦3個不同層級官員的電話為林鄭拉票，有中聯辦副主任近日與建制政黨人士會面，表明中央支持林鄭，大讚她有能力，又批評曾俊華做事不積極，更當面提出希望他們能出席林鄭的造勢大會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然林鄭行情看漲，但專欄引述部分工商界別選委私下討論，工商界不少選委已私下表明即使提名林鄭，投票時會支持曾俊華，預料緊跟中央立場的選委，與「表裏不一」的選委數目相若。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56219835&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56219835%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170125&d=K%2FtronHRi6BLACeVraY2JGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9e7eba58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56219835%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170125&h=a1b05e35\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56219835&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170125</a>"},{"pid":"80419ba58c23dad3fa876cc0119a6d5411f38266","tid":94153,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:02:31.000Z","msg":"林奠 = 中央<br />\n<br />\n林奠治港 = 中央治港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f670ed3f87b26372ab9e69704dd32c7c669e14ee","tid":94153,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"不撐林鄭視為支持港獨"},{"pid":"1c0c1a336708df987cb36937ca90602e4350575e","tid":94153,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"上屆佢先話唐唐無走票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52c8b7eaf78bc5522ea2db9865fbb3df82836cc","tid":94153,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上屆佢先話唐唐無走票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}